{"tid":1822688,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"據報新地 (00016.HK) 郭基煇建議單程證上限削半至每日75人 為期三年","createTime":"2020-01-13T06:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T08:48:43.000Z","uid":55390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"75546e859360030825503b42e268f6274ba08fe6","tid":1822688,"uid":55390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:11:45.000Z","msg":"廣東省政協十二屆三次會議昨日(12日)在廣州開幕。據《南華早報》報道，廣東政協常委、新地(<a href=\"http://00016.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00016.HK&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyAV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=2a73a7a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00016.HK</a>)執行董事郭基煇向內地與會人員提交一份報告，建議每日透過單程證來港人數上限削半，由每日150人下調至75人。<br />\n<br />\n該報告總結了郭氏參與成立的香港廣東青年總會在2017至2019年間的調查，指近年本港本土主義興起，及本地年輕人對內地政制的誤解，令年輕人不願意與大灣區融合，而反修例運動加劇了有關情緒。<br />\n<br />\n報告稱，每日150單程證配額是本港與內地關係的痛點，他建議三年先導計劃，每日配額上限削半至75人。報告稱，該象徵行為具重大影響，讓本港年輕人看到及感到中央政府的關心。(da/u)~<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.986665/latest-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-content%2FNOW.986665%2Flatest-news&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyAV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=9234c141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.986665/latest-news</a><br />\n<br />\n連登仔點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0672ce47af80bab1182b5c2ddabefb9cc44f8140","tid":1822688,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6863f6d436c6c3ad92bd4ed58b7525885953c5","tid":1822688,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:13:50.000Z","msg":"Cut晒"},{"pid":"3df0d883f317d3298bcdfd754518e81e58901e01","tid":1822688,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:14:16.000Z","msg":"同港鐵一樣 <br />\n今年唔加價比住優惠你先<br />